      "user": "bea_bop",
      "slug": "splatter-horror",
      "title": "Splatter Horror",
      "desc": "Splatter horror commonly delivers on showcasing extremely (sometimes to the point of hilarious absurdity) transgressive, viscerally gruesome acts of Grand Guignol violence and subsequent revulsion usually through the employment of special effects. Almost as an unspoken rule, they also tend to display a fascination with the vulnerability of the human body and the theatricality of its mutilation in numerous ways.\nOften the genre is associated with but not exclusive to another genres such the slasher, exploitation, body horror, comedy and even science fiction, but others may blur the lines.",
